  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK325">
<l>nilaiyañci nīttāru ḷellāṅ kolaiyañcik</l>
<l>kollāmai cūḻvāṉ ṟalai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of all those who, fearing the permanence of earthly births, have abandoned desire, he is the chief who, fearing (the guilt of) murder, considers how he may avoid the destruction of life.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
